<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><?ish ishref="GUID-157DC275-D299-436E-8FB4-C562B350561C" version="1" lang="en-US"?><task xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="GUID-157DC275-D299-436E-8FB4-C562B350561C" xml:lang="en-US" ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3" domains="(topic task)                            (topic hi-d)                            (topic ui-d)                            (topic sw-d)                            (topic indexing-d)                            (topic ut-d)                            a(base ishcondition)                            a(base varid)                            a(base varref)                            a(base cid)                            a(base partslist)                            (topic oce-d)                            (topic sdlVariables-c)                            (topic oceCommonElements-c)                            (topic oceMetaDecl-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c task oceTask-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c hi-d oceHighlight-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c ui-d oceUi-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c sw-d oceSoftware-c)   " class="- topic/topic task/task "><title translate="yes" class="- topic/title "> Printing is not possible</title><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Diagnostics</category></metadata></prolog><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><section id="M140852-B298" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Symptom</title><p class="- topic/p ">A job is submitted with the RIP, but printing is not possible (the RIP is unable to transfer the data to the printer). 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">The network connection is OK as ping is working and the Settings Editor can be used. 
</p></section><section id="GUID-3B8895B9-6BB9-45A4-B224-251952987CAD" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Possible cause</title><p class="- topic/p "> The system is not licensed (no base license installed). 
</p></section><section id="SECTION_BC4C9DB1335C400D8CFB6D62C2406122" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Tests/Checks</title><p class="- topic/p ">Check the license in the Settings Editor. For a licensed system this has to look like: 
</p><fig id="GUID-DF254EED-85A4-4D88-AD38-FEBB8A410084" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-BC4E1BAB-CD61-4542-A611-B8F52E0BEE19-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-BC4E1BAB-CD61-4542-A611-B8F52E0BEE19-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p "> You can also check the datalog. If the base license is missing, the datalog will report this: 
</p><fig id="GUID-4035EA55-725E-4B3C-81BD-EB7510DC235F" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-151EA875-60D0-432D-A864-DCFE2C9944EF-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-151EA875-60D0-432D-A864-DCFE2C9944EF-low.png"/></fig></section><section id="GUID-2BB63C78-AC2A-41E6-9B4A-78458E4FD184" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Solutions</title><p class="- topic/p ">. 
</p></section><section id="GUID-4316C372-BAE7-48E5-9838-EF6E72EDC90E" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "> Case 1: The field “ID of license dongle” is not empty</title><fig id="GUID-1F981191-DD48-4C30-A783-1E3D33632BCC" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-5C82C9B7-8D42-408E-AA77-2B211D308DAC-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-5C82C9B7-8D42-408E-AA77-2B211D308DAC-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p ">You need to get a license for this printer. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">For additional info see : 
<xref keyref="GENINSTALLLICENSE001" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-83541379-2C72-4191-948E-292B66F16EE2.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text How to request a license?>How to request a license</xref> / 
<xref keyref="GENINSTLICENCE002" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-A5731826-4ADE-4A39-807A-9F6B14629783.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text How to install a license?>Install a license received via e-mail</xref> 
</p></section><section id="GUID-326577AA-A3F2-4A17-8E8D-E4BC4E9315BE" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "> Case 2: The field “ID of license dongle” is empty</title><fig id="GUID-73EA3C6A-7D32-416A-A42E-C078D633E489" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-0B4F12A7-4D8B-462D-8EAD-EA186D6BBB84-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-0B4F12A7-4D8B-462D-8EAD-EA186D6BBB84-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p ">Either the license dongle is not present or it is not working properly. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">First, you need to arrange a new license dongle. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> Then install it and arrange a license for the printer with this dongle. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">For additional info see : 
<xref keyref="GENINSTALLLICENSE001" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-83541379-2C72-4191-948E-292B66F16EE2.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text How to request a license?>How to request a license</xref> / 
<xref keyref="GENINSTLICENCE002" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-A5731826-4ADE-4A39-807A-9F6B14629783.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text How to install a license?>Install a license received via e-mail</xref> 
</p></section><section id="GUID-4EA563EF-08AC-4D75-B86A-9C6318998517" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Possible cause</title><p class="- topic/p "> The system has serial number 0.
</p></section><section id="GUID-F6C0F4A0-8054-43C8-9C90-6888B3A8761B" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Test/Check</title><p class="- topic/p "> In case of serial number 0:
</p><p class="- topic/p "> Call the regional service organization and escalate to HQ.
</p></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-E6576A00-297D-4384-A53F-5DDD5C6F199D.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Observation</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
</task>